Keep the kids entertained at Ster-Kinekor i’langa this festive season by taking them to see the latest installment in the Spider-Man movieverse. Synopsis: Phil Lord and Christopher Miller, the creative minds behind The Lego Movie and 21 Jump Street, bring their unique talents to a fresh vision of a different Spider-Man Universe, with a groundbreaking visual style that’s the first of its kind. Spider-Man™: Into the Spider-Verse introduces Brooklyn teen Miles Morales, and the limitless possibilities of the Spider-Verse, where more than one can wear the mask. Starring: Shameik Moore, Hailee Steinfeld, Jake Johnson, Liev Schreiber and Lily Tomlin Directed by: Bob Persichetti, Peter Ramsey and Rodney Rothman       